{
    "headline": "Margaret's Keftedes (Greek Meatballs)",
    "name": "Margaret's Keftedes (Greek Meatballs)",
    "description": "This is my yia yia's recipe--a family favorite straight from the village of Kyparissia. Serve as an appetizer or with tzatziki, Greek salata, and pita or pasta for a full meal. They taste best served at room temp and make for wonderful leftovers. If you don't care for lamb, try using all beef instead.",
    "recipeCuisine": [
        "Greek"
    ],
    "totalTime": "PT55M",
    "cookTime": "PT30M",
